                  <span class="">p166(因為坊市的嚴格規定，無法滿足農村的交換需求)a separate system of unofficial markets...gradually grew up in the countryside to cater for the needs of the farmers...The old system gave way during the ninth century to an era of vastly increased commercial freedom.
...The Chinese rural economy was becoming linked with the market mechanism. Trade was no longer just the supplier of luxuries (as in ...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-20 09:15</span>
                  
